While I knew of Penn and Teller, I had not seen any of their shows, in person or on TV. I loved every minute of their performance last night. They had me laughing most of the time, and their tricks were amazing. Thought it was a very nice touch that they took selfies and signed autographs at the end of their show.  Tip: I was able to purchase our seats at a discount through Travelzoo.

